---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout 
  title="Frequently Asked Questions | Complete Health Peptides"
  description="Find answers to common questions about our products, shipping, returns, and research information."
>
  <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-700 to-secondary-700 text-white py-16">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-heading font-bold mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>
      <p class="text-xl max-w-3xl">Find answers to the most common questions about our products and services.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-12">
    <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-sm p-8 mb-8">
      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="mb-8">Our comprehensive FAQ is available in our documentation center. Please click the button below to view the complete FAQ.</p>
        
        <div class="flex justify-center my-8">
          <a 
            href="https://docs.chpeptides.com/faq.html" 
            target="_blank" 
            rel="noopener noreferrer" 
            class="bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-md font-medium text-lg transition inline-flex items-center"
          >
            View Complete FAQ
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" class="h-5 w-5 ml-2" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="currentColor">
              <path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 5.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l4 4a1 1 0 010 1.414l-4 4a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L12.586 11H5a1 1 0 110-2h7.586l-2.293-2.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd" />
            </svg>
          </a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-10">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Product Questions</h2>
            
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-4">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">What are your products used for?</h3>
                <p>Our products are intended for laboratory research use only. They are not for human or veterinary use, therapeutic applications, or diagnostic purposes.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-4">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">How are your peptides manufactured?</h3>
                <p>Our peptides are synthesized using solid phase peptide synthesis (SPPS) technology under strict quality control protocols to ensure high purity and consistency.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-4">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Do you provide Certificates of Analysis?</h3>
                <p>Yes, we provide Certificates of Analysis (CoA) for all our research products. These can be accessed from your account after purchase.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Ordering & Shipping</h2>
            
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-4">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">How long does shipping take?</h3>
                <p>Standard shipping typically takes 3-5 business days within the continental US. International shipping can take 7-14 business days depending on the destination.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-4">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Do you ship internationally?</h3>
                <p>Yes, we ship to most international locations. Please note that customers are responsible for any duties or taxes imposed by their country.</p>
              </div>
              
              <div class="border-b border-gray-200 pb-4">
                <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">What payment methods do you accept?</h3>
                <p>We accept all major credit cards, PayPal, and cryptocurrency payments. For institutional orders, we can also accept purchase orders and wire transfers.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gray-100 p-6 rounded-lg my-8">
          <p class="font-semibold">For the complete FAQ with more detailed answers, please refer to our documentation center by clicking the button above.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>